Focus on sparking conversations 
Mix up content formats
Post at time audience is most active
engage consistently and authentically : in a way that adds value

1. Advice, Milestones, learnings
	: walk people through the process
	: Importance of milestones
	: Actionable learnings that others can apply

2. Industry moments/news
	: find something everyone is talking about [#hashtag]

3. Teach something new
4. Events, Conferences & Launches

