Professional milestones & company news:
	- write in first person
	- focus on the why
	- tag relevant people

Staty consistent

---

1. How will my content help someone succeed
2. Why would someone be interested in this post 
	: if they dont know me or my work
3. Focus on what you are qualified to speak about

---

Break up complex topics into a series of posts
Back up your points with examples and data
Cite your sources

--

Use @tags to connect - not as growth hacks
Visuals [photos, infrographics, charts, shortform video]
Use visuals to reinforce your message

---

Start your post with a hook
End a post with a clear CTA
Engage in the community you want to build
Leave comments on other people's posts 
Reply thoughtfully to comments in your posts
Create content on topics you know members are gonna care about

--


The 3-2-1 model calls for a weekly breakdown of three pieces of industry-related content, two pieces of “proud” content (positivity for your employees or community), and one piece promoting your brand or solutions.